A Vaulted Foyer~
~
The antechamber of this temple is adorned with grand white marble and green 
malachite carvings to either side of the room.  The still figures of unknown 
scholars and sages with arms reaching skyward support the thirty-foot tall 
ceiling.  Each of the statues wears a giant glowing amulet of Graal 
around it's neck, providing adequate lighting for this grand chamber.  
~
