The Gallery - North Wing~
~
Displayed items within this section of the gallery include those of arcane 
nature.  Within the center of the room is a large pool of liquid.  High 
above this pool many scintillating, prismatic shards of crystal levitate 
mysteriously.  Upon a stand along the east wall, a dragon-shaped ice 
sculpture remains unharmed by a blazing shroud of magical flames.  More 
items are on display in the south wing of the gallery as well.  
~
